SOCIAL NETWORK CONNECT
If you use one of our applications and
connect to your social network account, such as Facebook, Twitter, Vine,
Instagram, YouTube and so on, within such application, you will be providing us
with basic account information i.e., user ID, name, email, gender, birthday,
current city, profile picture URL and the user IDs of your friends who have
also connected with our applications. In addition, we will cache data we
receive from the Social Network APIs to improve our user experience. If you
want us to delete the data we receive from social networks about you, please
contact us at support:
sadik.aslandag.app@gmail.com
.
