for the privacy practices of such Linked Sites, and this Privacy Policy does
not apply to such Linked Sites. The operators of Linked Sites may collect
information about you, and may use and disclose that information. We encourage
you to review the privacy policies of the Linked Sites that you use.
OPT-IN AND OPT-OUT POLICY
We will not share your personal
information in ways other than as described in this Privacy Policy unless you
